name: Orcustrated Einsatz
desc: If your opponent Normal or Special Summons a monster(s) (except during the Damage Step): You can take 1 "Orcust" or "World Legacy" monster from your hand or Deck, and either send it to the GY or banish it. You can only use this effect of "Orcustrated Einsatz" once per turn.
str3: Do you want to send it to the graveyard?
